gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Oh God, oh God, Brahma's mind thoughts, you say all are ornaments; 
The divine Indra tied with Sur and Savar, Manu Kashyap with Ravi Chand.

Here is the translation:

It will go back to divine path, I say, it will find happiness there; 
Thus said Durvasa Muni, he did an entry into Kailas before.
